             was indicted for <rs id="t18010114-44-off246" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010114-44-off246" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010114-44-off246" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010114-44-cd247" type="crimeDate">5th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010114-44-off246 t18010114-44-cd247"></join>, six pounds of moist sugar, value 4s. and seven pounds of other sugar, value 8s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010114-44-victim440" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Roebuck
                  <interp inst="t18010114-44-victim440" type="surname" value="Roebuck"></interp>
